channel.title: My server will only let me in and not others, port 43594 will not open!
channel.description:
I HAVE PORTFORWARDED AND WENT TO PORTFORWARD.COM- i have foloed guides everything. yes i have no-ip- i have a WRT54G2 linksys router, i have portforwarded. ive download jdku11 and everything my main problem is. Port 43594 wont open, so i can log in and others cant! PLEASE HELP OR MESSAGE ME AT dudedidyouseethat1@hotmail.com i will do anything to make a server, ive been trying for a very long time. PLEASE HELP. - ive even bought the new router for 60$ just for a server...
